Michael H Thaman's Experience
Title: Chief Financial Officer
               Company: Corning Incorporated
Job Details
               Company Size: $1 bil and above - Employee Range: 5,000 to less than 25,000. Owens Corning (NYSE: OC) develops, manufactures and markets insulation, roofing, and fiberglass composites. Global in scope and human in scale, the company's market-leading businesses use their deep expertise in materials, manufacturing and building science to develop products and systems that save energy and improve comfort in commercial and residential buildings.  Through its glass reinforcements business, the company makes thousands of products lighter, stronger and more durable.  Ultimately Owens Corning people and products make the world a better place.  Based in Toledo, Ohio, Owens Corning posted 2014 sales of $5.3 billion and employs about 14,000 people in 25 countries.  It has been listed as a Fortune 500(r) company for more than 60 consecutive years.  For more information, please visit www.owenscorning.com.
Title: Chief Executive Officer
               Company: Corning Incorporated
Job Details
               Owens Corning (NYSE: OC) develops, manufactures and markets insulation, roofing, and fiberglass composites. Global in scope and human in scale, the company's market-leading businesses use their deep expertise in materials, manufacturing and building science to develop products and systems that save energy and improve comfort in commercial and residential buildings.  Through its glass reinforcements business, the company makes thousands of products lighter, stronger and more durable.  Ultimately Owens Corning people and products make the world a better place.  Based in Toledo, Ohio, Owens Corning posted 2014 sales of $5.3 billion and employs about 14,000 people in 25 countries.  It has been listed as a Fortune 500(r) company for more than 60 consecutive years.  For more information, please visit www.owenscorning.com.
